In the MATTER OF the VOCATIONAL ASSISTANCE DISPUTE OF Bernardita MCTIGRIT, Claimant. Bernardita McTigrit, Petitioner,
v.
SAIF Corporation; and Alternative Services Oregon, Inc., Respondents. A162336 Court of Appeals of Oregon. Argued and submitted October 31, 2018.
January 3, 2019 Bennett P. Dalton, Oregon City, argued the cause for petitioner. Also on the briefs were Bennett P. Dalton, L.L.C., and The Dalton Law Firm. David L. Runner, Salem, argued the cause and filed the brief for respondents. Before Ortega, Presiding Judge, and Powers, Judge, and Garrett, Judge pro tempore. PER CURIAM

Reversed. Chu v. SAIF , 290 Or. App. 194 , 415 P.3d 68 , rev. den. , 363 Or. 677 , 427 P.3d 1089 (2018).
